Operations

=   ->      foti/fota

+   ->      fawi / fawa

-   ->      fawti / fawta

x   ->      laavi (laabi en prononciation francaise) / laawa

/   ->      lawti / lawta

^   ->      ngol / ngola

√   ->      ngolti / ngolta

<   ->      baawo

>   ->      yeyso

==  ->      feppi

!=  ->      feppah

<=  ->      baawo maa feppi

>=  ->      yeyso maa feppi


Examples:
2 + 3 = 5
didi fawi tati foti jowi

5 - 1 = 4
jowi fawti goo foti nayi

3 x 4 = 12
tati laavi nayi foti = sappo didi

6 / 2 = 3
jey-goo lawti didi foti tati

2 ^ 3 = 8
didi ngol tati foti jey-tati
2 ^ 3 = 2 * 2 * 2

 9 √ 2 = 3  (racine n-ieme)
 jeynay ngolti didi foti tati
 (ca s'ecrit aussi: 9^-2 = 3  
 16 ^ -4 = 4
 sappo jey goo ngolti nayi foti nayi
 
